500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2518\n```\n\n#### Argilla Store\n\nThe Argilla Store allows you to sync your observations to [Argilla](https://argilla.io/). To use it, you first need to create a [free Argilla deployment on Hugging Face](https://docs.argilla.io/latest/getting_started/quickstart/). Take a look at [the example](./examples/argilla_example.py) for more details.\n\n![Argilla Store](./assets/argilla.png)\n\n## Contributing\n\nSee [CONTRIBUTING.md](./CONTRIBUTING.md)\n"], "modules": [{"name": "observers.observers.models.aisuite", "documentation": [], "functions": [{"name": "observers.observers.models.aisuite.wrap_aisuite", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "client", "type": {"name": "Client", "xref": {"fqname": "aisuite.Client", "project": null}, "params": null}, "default": null}, {"name": "store", "type": {"name": "Optional", "xref": {"fqname": "typing.Optional", "project": "--std--"}, "params": [{"name": "Union", "xref": {"fqname": "typing.Union", "project": "--std--"}, "params": [{"name": "DatasetsStore", "xref": {"fqname": "observers.stores.datasets.DatasetsStore", "project": null}, "params": null}, {"name": "DuckDBStore", "xref": {"fqname": "observers.stores.duckdb.DuckDBStore", "project": null}, "params": null}]}]}, "default": "..."}, {"name": "tags", "type": {"name": "Optional", "xref": {"fqname": "typing.Optional", "project": "--std--"}, "params": [{"name": "List", "xref":